as illustrated by 
<bibRefCitation author="Williams, R. C., Jr. &amp; E. L. Bell" box="[192,505,1603,1627]" pageId="30" pageNumber="29" pagination="121 - 140" refId="ref37020" refString="Williams, R. C., Jr., and E. L. Bell. 1940. New Neotropical Hesperiidae and notes on others (Lepidoptera). Transactions of the American Entomological Society 66: 121 - 140." type="journal article" year="1940">Williams and Bell (1940)</bibRefCitation>
